        |---------------| <---greshape ---> |------------------|
        | 1   2   1   2 |                   | 1    1  3   2  4 |
        | 1   2   3   4 |                   | 2    5  7   6  8 |
        | 2   1   5   6 |                   +------------------+
        | 2   2   7   8 |
        +---------------+
*/

    di `how' _col(9) " {it:long}" _skip(33) "{it:wide}"
